author: jvanzyl
msg: o use canonical file when getting the tempdir if you're going to compare using canonical file. on many unices
including os/x "/tmp" is actually "/private/tmp" so all the comparisons of System.getProperty( "java.io.tmpdir" ) fail
becasuse that will return "/tmp" unless to make a file of it and ask for the canonical value.
